r>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PROTECT YOUR BACKPACK - ASR Outdoor backpack rain cover is made of durable, high-quality polyester waterproof materials to protect your bag from inclement weather. Ideal for traveling, camping, hiking and getting to and from school</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ADJUSTABLE DRAWSTRING CLOSURE - Backpack cover comes with an adjustable drawstring closure for a snug, custom fit for any standard travel bag or backpack. Easily adjusts to completely cover your backpack, ideal for adults and children</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">LIGHTWEIGHT AND EASY TO CLEAN - Rain gear bag cover weighs just .2lbs and can be spot cleaned with soap and water. Just wipe it down after use and hang it to dry before next use. Easily fold it and store it with your other rain gear when not in use once dry</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FITS MOST BACKPACKS - Rain cover expands up to 28” x 7” x 17.5” that will fit most backpacks and travel bags. High-visibility blue rain cover is easy to spot in a crowd, great for keeping an eye on kids during large gatherings and parades</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - Color: blue; Material: waterproof polyester; Dimensions: 28” x 7” x 17.5”; Weight: .2lbs (3.2oz); Cleaning: spot clean with soap and water, hang to dry; Adjustable fit; Closure type: drawstring</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Waterproof Backpack Cover Adjustable Fit Camping Essentials - Blue</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">14.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>The ASR Outdoor backpack cover was designed to protect your backpack from inclement weather, making it ideal for camping, hiking, traveling or getting to and from school. It’s made of high-quality, durable waterproof polyester to keep your bag dry even during a storm.\n\nThe backpack rain cover comes with an adjustable drawstring closure for a custom and snug fit that will work with most standard sized travel bags and backpacks. It will easily adjust to completely cover your backpack, making it a great option for both adults and children.\n\nDesigned to be lightweight and compact when not in use, this backpack cover weighs just .2lbs so it won’t add too much weight to your backpack. It can be spot cleaned with soap and water - just weipe it down after use and hand it to dry before you need it next. \n\nOur bag cover expands up to 28” x 7” x 17.5” and comes in a high-visilbity bright blue color that is easy to spot in a crowd, ideal for keeping an eye on kids during large gatherings like parades and school trips. Make sure to grab one of these before your next camping or hiking trip, or keep it in your travel gear in case of a rainy day!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n